        "actor_id": 2,
        "actor_name": "WeakSoul",
        "filename": "WeakSoulBeingSoothed_node2.wav",
        "text": "……谢谢你……让我想起来……生前也有人……这样对我笑过……"
      }
    ],
    "tts_backend": "qwen3-tts-flash"
  },
  {
    "dialogue_name": "虚弱游魂对话",
    "file_name": "WeakSoulDialogue",
    "audio_files": [
      {
        "node_id": 0,
        "actor_id": 2,
        "actor_name": "WeakSoul",
        "filename": "WeakSoulDialogue_node0.wav",
        "text": "......谢谢你......那温暖的光芒......让我想起了生前......"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 1,
        "actor_id": 0,
        "actor_name": "Player",
        "filename": "WeakSoulDialogue_node1.wav",
        "text": "你是谁？为什么会在这里徘徊？"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 2,
        "actor_id": 2,
        "actor_name": "WeakSoul",
        "filename": "WeakSoulDialogue_node2.wav",
        "text": "我......我已经不记得自己的名字了......只记得......饥饿......无尽的饥饿......"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 3,
        "actor_id": 2,
        "actor_name": "WeakSoul",
        "filename": "WeakSoulDialogue_node3.wav",
        "text": "你的光芒让我感到安宁......我想......我可以安心地离去了......"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 5,
        "actor_id": 2,
        "actor_name": "WeakSoul",
        "filename": "WeakSoulDialogue_node5.wav",
        "text": "谢谢你......引魂之人......愿你的光芒照亮更多迷失的灵魂......"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 6,
        "actor_id": 2,
        "actor_name": "WeakSoul",
        "filename": "WeakSoulDialogue_node6.wav",
        "text": "你有一颗善良的心......愿孟婆大人的指引与你同在......"
      }
    ],
    "tts_backend": "qwen3-tts-flash"
  },
