  {
    "dialogue_name": "NewDialogue",
    "file_name": "孟忘和佃户",
    "audio_files": [
      {
        "node_id": 0,
        "actor_id": 5,
        "actor_name": "TenantFarmer",
        "filename": "孟忘和佃户_node0.wav",
        "text": "小后生，你来干嘛"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 1,
        "actor_id": 5,
        "actor_name": "TenantFarmer",
        "filename": "孟忘和佃户_node1.wav",
        "text": "哦，你是那道士的徒弟吧，我跟你说，你师傅那符纸可真灵。"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 2,
        "actor_id": 5,
        "actor_name": "TenantFarmer",
        "filename": "孟忘和佃户_node2.wav",
        "text": "那女鬼向前天天来偷米，气得我们老爷都肥成猪了还要出来守着粮食"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 3,
        "actor_id": 5,
        "actor_name": "TenantFarmer",
        "filename": "孟忘和佃户_node3.wav",
        "text": "结果你师傅那符一贴，粮食还真就没有少过"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 4,
        "actor_id": 5,
        "actor_name": "TenantFarmer",
        "filename": "孟忘和佃户_node4.wav",
        "text": "小师傅你今天来干嘛"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 6,
        "actor_id": 5,
        "actor_name": "TenantFarmer",
        "filename": "孟忘和佃户_node6.wav",
        "text": "哎，我也弄不灵清，收成一年年不好"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 8,
        "actor_id": 5,
        "actor_name": "TenantFarmer",
        "filename": "孟忘和佃户_node8.wav",
        "text": "老爷和管家都在困觉，现在不好招待"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 9,
        "actor_id": 5,
        "actor_name": "TenantFarmer",
        "filename": "孟忘和佃户_node9.wav",
        "text": "不过你进去坐会应该没啥问题"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 10,
        "actor_id": 5,
        "actor_name": "TenantFarmer",
        "filename": "孟忘和佃户_node10.wav",
        "text": "是你师傅要你来的吧"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 11,
        "actor_id": 5,
        "actor_name": "TenantFarmer",
        "filename": "孟忘和佃户_node11.wav",
        "text": "如果不用准备的话现在就可以去换"
      },
      {
        "node_id": 12,
        "actor_id": 5,
        "actor_name": "TenantFarmer",
        "filename": "孟忘和佃户_node12.wav",
        "text": "粮仓就在那边，符在门上"
      }
    ],
    "tts_backend": "qwen3-tts-flash"
  },
  {
    "dialogue_name": "NewDialogue",
    "file_name": "孟忘和渔夫",
    "audio_files": [
      {
        "node_id": 0,
        "actor_id": 0,
        "actor_name": "Player",
        "filename": "孟忘和渔夫_node0.wav",
